\insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066  girl hit me once and I come in crying. Well you are a coward she says - you go out and hit her back or else I'll hit you. We had a right ar
gument and I went out and pasted this - I'll never forget that - pasted this here girl and mother says that's right - you stick up for yourself love. And I did do after that you know, I thought if you hit me anybody now -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Do you ever remember your mother hitting you though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
Oh yes, yes. Oh yes. What was it I did once - and - oh she carried on to me, she didn't hit me so much - I don't know what it was that I did. I'll never forget it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You don't remember what it was though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 It'll come to me in a bit. Was something in a pram.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Were you taking a baby out in a pram?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
That. And me mother didn't think I was old enough you see to take this child. I said well, I'll stick to the handles - I won't leave go of the handles. I'll never forget that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 And she gave you a good hiding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes, for stick - for going with it at all you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 How did you feel about it - do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh, I felt shocking. I felt well it was ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You felt it was unfair did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes. I di
d. Because I thought if anything - and now when I can hear of that child left a girl going didn't she - she left a baby going up - that brought that back to me. Because - I had the instance of this child because I - I were a beggar for pushing it you see.
 I used to call and take it out - used to like wheeling pram. Now and again let it just go on }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid611988\charrsid12273066 its}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
 own. And I thought many a time when somebody was telling me about the one and I thought oh yes, and - I don't think I wheeled a baby in a pram since. But it was all right you see, I stopped - stopped taking it out then because - 'cos .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Because your mother was cross?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, she was very annoyed about it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 When you had a birthday would it be different from any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh yes. We used to
 have a little party and they're all coming in the yard you know. Oh little cups round the table - in the yard - oh we had ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Your mother used to make you a birthday party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh yes. Little buns and little sandwiches and a cake. Yes. I don't know where ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you have presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
Oh, well, they couldn't afford much you know. Ha'porth of sweets or something like that they'd bring you. I haven't had anything off me daughter.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you have guests in the back yard though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh, oh,
 oh they all used to congregate when they knew that getting cake and cup of tea, oh, they'd come in some of them non - non-invited guests'd walk in. My mother'd say come on in - the more the merrier.
