\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes, odd times I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 To the adult service?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes. I did}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid611988\charrsid12273066 . }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You went to Sunday school you told me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh, I went to Sunday school
