\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 That was a different one was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes, that was - oh well, we moved you see. When I got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10514531 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066  sort of thing.
