Well, me brothers used to start us off. Do you mean at home? Oh yes. Me brothers used to say now we'll say grace but the other elder ones wouldn't. I suppose they thought that they didn't need to say it, I don't know. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Were you taught to say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes. Always have to say your prayers.
