\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, I haven't had much of a life while my husbands been gone. I don't get out.
