\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 How did you get on with the rest of them?
