Oh, pretty fair you know, as long as you didn't rough 'em and let them all have their own way and if you didn't - if you didn't rough them they were all right, but if }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid611988\charrsid12273066 you roughed}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066  them they - put you in your place - 'cos I was youngest see.
