\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you do the washing at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Washing at home - when he was on nights I had to clean upstairs at night when he'd gone out. 'Cos he'd be sleeping all day you see.
