\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you make medicines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you bottle fruit or vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh yes, we'd bottle fruit - when it's in you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you grow any fruit or vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
He had an allotment you know. Yes. Through - just high up through the field. Oh, he'd spend hours at a time there when he wasn't working. Well, I think it was better because he'd want a bit of fresh air wouldn't he.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you buy any tinned or dried vegetables or fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, I don't think they went up for - in for it as much then - you can get anything now can't you in tins.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did he keep any livestock for the family - hens?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No, only the dog - only our }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6714541\charrsid12273066 Dutch}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 How many times a week did you eat meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
Oh, I don't know. Just depends 'cos we used to have to - you know - we couldn't cook meat and then warm it up again for father. We used to have fish and that you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You don't remember about how many times you had meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, a bit oftener than I do now because it was dear - it's dear now. Oh I think it's awfully dear don't you - meat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 When your daughter was young did you ever have tinned meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No, I don't think we did. You get fed up with it now but - it's better than nothing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 There wouldn't be any extra meat from poaching?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh no. Not like it now - they never ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you ever have to go short so that your child could have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes, yes. You know, Post Office wages weren'
t too good. They got - they worked up you see - he had to do. He had a pretty decent job towards the end. He carried on with it a few years before he did you know.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you give him a larger helping than yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh Lord - yes. You have to do with a man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 He's the breadwinner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What about table manners with your daughter?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh, she was nice at the table - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did she have to hold her knife and fork in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh yes, yes, yes. She was very good on that. She didn't need much training really but she did. She was very good Hilda was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did she have to sit in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes. No moving from the table 'til you'd finished and sit still.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you make her eat everything you put on her plate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well she - she didn't need any asking - she used to always save a bit for the dog you know. The dog always had to have it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Could she ask for a second helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 If there was any left she could.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Could she bring toys or a book to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh no. She can have them after. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You didn't all sit at a meal because your husband was a postman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, he was different times, you couldn't very well you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 But when your husband sat at the table who served the meal did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes. You know, we had a -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Who did you serve first?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Father. Sometimes if daughter was hungry she'd say can I get me own mum. Then she'd get up first.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did Hilda have a special chair when she was young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes, high chair - yes. And then -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 How old was she when she came to the table - do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh, she'd be about twelve months you know - they make a little mess don't they sometimes. She weren't so bad on feeding though.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 When she was young did you feel there was a right and a wrong way to bring up children - what were your ideas about bringing up children?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
Well, if they were good well then it's no trouble to bring them up but sometimes they get bit what they call cantankerous you know. They say now you won't have
 - you won't get your tea for a bit - I won't get it ready and then you used to be a shilabalu. And then they'd say - will you serve me first because dad can wait. She was a - I had to give her -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What did you consider was right and wrong when you bro
ught your girl up? What did you teach her was right and wrong and did it change from when you were little?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
No, I don't think so. She did - she didn't need much training. She was a good child. Yes. If she liked - if we give her something that she like
d you know and you give it to her about three times say I don't want any more of that mum or dad. What was her favourite? I'm just trying to think what was her favourite. She used to like chips you know. She'd have had chips at every meal - so - father wo
uld say has she been having chips. And it - you know - it's - well, I don't like - I like perhaps about once a week I have 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Weren't there certain things you considered right and certain things you thought were wrong?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Do you remember what they were when she was little?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, sometimes they get out of hand don't they which - is what they get - get learning off other children I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You mean she didn't obey you and this sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Now - now and again. Oh well s
o-and-so's mother doesn't smack her for that she'll say. I'd say oh well what her mother does and what your mother does is - her father used to be a bit strict you know, so I had to give way to her for a bit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Her father was stricter with her than you were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes. You know -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you both have the same ideas about bringing her up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No, she - he had one way and I don't think he should have had it like that because I -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What was the difference?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well - he'd pick her up at the least t
hing. The child wouldn't have get any home life if he'd have had his way. Go on you red-headed cinder - said he should he - mop of red hair he had. When she was born she'd red hair. Oh, I says, take her away - she's got red hair. They said well, father's 
got it so it's only - oh he was right red-headed. Lovely hair.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 But he was strict with her did you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 He was - well, he wasn't more strict - he was a bit short tempered you see. He hadn't the same patience as some of us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 And yet he used to pick her up a lot?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh yes, yes, he had.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 So he was good to her in a lot of ways?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Who did you talk to if you were ever worried about her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, you - I used to say to here now I'll tell your father when he comes in. Then she - she'd check - check it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Say she wasn't well and you were worried - did you ever have anyone you could talk to - how about your mother-in-law?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 His mother - well, we never saw so much of her - she had a grocers shop. She hadn't even time to come to the wedding. No. Well, she }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10514531 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066  a second time and he wasn't much good this chap who }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10514531 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066  her - don't know.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What things did you feel you ought to do for your child - in the way of affection - were you very affectionate with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes, o
h yes. If he was to just say something sharp to her and - and she'd come out to me if I was out you see, and she'd wait while I'd been out and I come back. She said me dads been shouting at me. I said well, what have you done. Well, I - I don't know, she'
d say. I'd say oh you must know. She'd done something you know and he'd say - he hadn't any patience at all. He was a good father you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you teach her things about safety or were there any special things that you felt you ought to do for Hilda as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
Well, no. Only the ordinary things, yes. Well, you see, I didn't get many - no mother. Well, I used to do better, you know, things for Hilda that I didn't get done for myself because I found out that -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What things were these - do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
Well, I daren't go on any - any other, children were going on these things from Sunday school you know. Oh you can't go on them of course - they'd no father - whether it was the expense or not I don't know. I never went on any picnics. And 
if I got one thing from Father Christmas that was enough - I didn't get any more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 How about Hilda - what did she get for Christmas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh, she got all the lot, I think, Hilda. Oh she got a lot of nice things when she come along that I }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6714541\charrsid12273066 didn\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 She got a lot of presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 If she had worries did you like her to come to you and talk about them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh yes, she'd come to me but she wouldn't go to her father. I had ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 How did you think she should behave towards you - were you very strict with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, I was and I wasn't sort of thing. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6714541\charrsid12273066 
I used to think well, if you nickel-nackle at them you know they don't get any life do they - child. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 I used to give way to her but her father didn't you know - he was a bit - his mother us
ed to be strict with him and I think that's where he found it out you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 When she was young did you both ever manage to get out together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No, we used to go - I'd take her to the Manley Park you know, Leicester Road, Higher Broughton. I'd take 
her there and now and again I'd - I'd take her - if he was off duty one night for the Sunday - we'd go to Heaton Park. I'll never forget going one Sunday and when we gets there - I never took any money out with me - when we get there, with him changing hi
s trousers he'd no money and we had to walk home. I've never - I'll never forget that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 But did you never get out with your husband on your own at night to go anywhere - did you never have a babysitter?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well we - oh didn't have babysitters in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you never have relatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Or anyone to look after her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No. Her father didn't believe in that. Say no, you get these children he said you must look after them. Well -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Was she allowed to join in if adults were talking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
Well, she was if it was like - you know, fit for children. We never had many in because our dad doing sort of night work you've got to keep the place quiet you see, while he gets - he must have his sleep. If I've seen hawkers coming down the str
eet I've gone up and asked them hot to knock at the door. I used to do when I was here - when we were over here when he was on nights.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What did you bring her up to consider important in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Going to Sunday school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You thought that was important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes, I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Suppose someone hit her did you tell her to hit back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes. I think that was the best way ors else they'd have got -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Were there any children you ever stopped her playing with - was she allowed to play with anyone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
No, because some of them - learnt her to talk rude and do - swearing and that you know in those days. We - you couldn't do with that you know, you got to check 'em up a bit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you ever punish her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh yes, if she did anything wrong because ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Who did the punishing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
Well, me, I used to shake her a bit say well now if you do this again you go to bed. Well, she never did it again. We hadn't much trouble with her though - she wasn't a troublesome child.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Not very often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 N
o. She always run to mother when it was anything wrong you know. Father - well he didn't have much time to be with her with him being on nights and sometimes he was on at six o'clock at night 'til six o'clock in the morning. Well, six o'clock you see she'
s been in for her tea and gone out to play and then he's gone off to work you see. She never saw very much of him when she was ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did he ever punish her though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh yes. If - if she did anything wrong he would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What did he do - did he shake her like you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes. Shake her - shout at - shout at her and shake her. That was all - he never hit her. A word was enough from him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Would you think that Hilda received her ideas about how she had to behave from you or from you and your husband together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, it was me because I had more to do with her than he had you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you work after you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10514531 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh no. Couldn't do - with him being on nights and that and - I used to take the child to school twice a day - up to the s
chool at the top - used to take her a drink in the morning you know for lunch I'd no sooner get home and then -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You used to go back to school with her drink did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes. And an odd time when they put him on days I had to be off then for meat a
nd get it on to stew and have it ready and his sandwiches ready to take with him for his tea. You'd no time to breathe. Take the poor old dog with me all the errands. I had to laugh at that old dog - oh - it was a collie you know. I used to take Hilda to 
s
chool and then go and get me meat and put it on - the dog used to come with me and then I'd put the meat on and by the time I'd just got perhaps a bit of dusting done then it was time to bring her back from school. So - I thought now one day I'll - I'll g
o up to the Post office for some stamps - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4214451\charrsid12273066 common}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
 Dutch - and it always used to wait outside the Post Office for me coming out - it never went in you see and then it'd waggle along after me - it was getting old - and one day I got home and I found out that -
 the dog was missing. Oh, I thought, where's the dog? So, then I though, Oh she's not here - it's funny.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 So where eventually did you find the dog?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 So I thought, well, I'll have to go all that way back now, across two dangerous crossings. And whe
n I got there what do you think? Two hours after that was. The poor thing was laid on the flags there - it had missed me coming out. And it never went 'til I - oh, and it did cry when I went back. It could have found }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6714541\charrsid12273066 its}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066  way easy enough - home - but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What happened when Hilda had a birthday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh, they had all the children you know. Yes. Oh we had to have the table extended and jam butties and jelly you know. Bit of cake.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did she have presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh Lord - aye. She used to have ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 So it was different to your childhood?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh Lord - aye. I know, nobody ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What kind of presents did she have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, dolls and - and - little things - tiddlywinks and all that you know. Little things like they had - oh the house was cluttered
 with this stuff.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What happened at Christmas - you had a party you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh yes. We had all - we had dad's brothers and sisters you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 And his mother you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Aye, his mother, yes, 'til she died.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you give each other Christmas presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
Oh yes. Do you know what they bought us for our Christmas - our birth - wedding present? His father that died - aspidistra plant. I says - I says - good Lord, I said - is that all your mother thinks we were - and aspidistra. Week after h
e says where's the aspidistra plant? He says, but I can tell you the answer before you tell me. I said, it's in the bin.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Your daughter learned to play the piano - did anyone else play a musical instrument
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Dad - dad'd - no, no. He'd play }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6714541\charrsid12273066 from ear}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066  you know. By ear.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 The piano?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes. But Hilda ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 And your daughter learned to play?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 She just learned to play the piano did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Aye - that was enough. It was expense that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did any of you sing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh, only bet
ween ourselves, you know. I've seen us have a party Christmas Day and it'll last while Boxing Day. Lard on the floor asleep - all night after - our dad says after the first year we were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10514531 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066  they did that and I was ill. Stopping up all that time and waiting on that lot. And some of them went home and then they come back again for breakfast time - for their breakfast.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 So you had all your husbands relatives and friends and you had the party and it went on all night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes, yes. Oh all night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 And then they went home for a bit and came back for breakfast and it went on Boxing Day, is this what you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 And you made music then together did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh yes. I - well Hilda played - well she couldn't play very much then becau
se - when was she born - at the February you see. No, they - they entertained themselves you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What did you do after Hilda was born though on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, just have a little one on our own and some of her little friends from the stre
et you see. But then - as she got older we had these - dads }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6714541\charrsid12273066 pals}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
 you know. We had two from his work and then his own brothers - he'd two or three brothers and they'd have their girls or their wives there. We did very well. I said but never no more of those
 though. It was doing too much. A great big potato pie in the bowl and then you'd all go out Christmas Ever New years eve to let the new year in you'd hear the town hall they'd - oh they linked across the road.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 This was new years eve you made your potato pie?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Let the new year in. No, let the new year in. All come in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you play games with Hilda when she was little and did your husband ever play games with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh yes. No, he didn't - he hadn't time daddy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 But you used to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
Oh yes, there was only me to do it - he - he - you know - it took him all his time and if he'd chance of any extra hours he used to do it to make a bit of money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you have a lot of books in your home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What about newspapers and magazines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh yes, we used to have them you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did your books come from the library?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No, never had any from the library.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you read aloud to each other?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 To Hilda - to Hilda but not do dad - he'd - he never mixed so much you know him being working and that different times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You used to read aloud to Hilda?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 I used to read to her. Then she'd read to me you see and I'd fall asleep - I'm not going to read to me mother she tumbles in her sleep.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you take Hilda out visiting neighbours or friends or relatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
Oh yes, we used to go about in the pram you know - with a pram. Take her to Heaton Park very often to take our tea you see, if dad was on days and he wouldn't be coming - he'd be on two 'til ten well, the
n it would give us a chance to get out a bit you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did dad ever go with you visiting relatives or friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No, very rare.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you take her shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes, if she was off school. I would take her in the morning and the dog when she wasn't schooling you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did Hilda never go out with just her father or did he take her out now and again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Now and again. He'd take her - if it was a Sunday off he'd come to Heaton Park you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 But he never took her out alone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Very rare. He used to take her to the allotment you know - her and the dog.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 So he did take her out alone then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes. Now, well if he was going - it was just when he was off at - you know - in the day and he'd take her and the dog. And she'd have a li
ttle plot on her own, you know. Flowers - flowers she put in herself you see - he used to buy her this packet of seeds and that was her garden. And a man come one day and he says - could you sell me a bunch off that plot there. Indeed I couldn't he said -
 I couldn't let you have one of them - one flower for a pound he said - they're my daughters. And it was her little garden.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 So he did take her out then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh, just up the - it was only in the next street but one you know. He wouldn't like dress up 
and do - he'd be tired but he wouldn't be tidy enough to go to Heaton Park. Oh, it was nice there and she got - and he - he planted some gladiolas one time - just the seeds you know - bulbs or whatever they are - and they were coming up beautiful and a ma
n
 says could you sell me a tuppenny bunch of flowers and put a few gladioli in? And I think one of the bulbs'd cost you about a shilling in those days. Dad says - I'm giving up gardening after that. And he used to give all the stuff that he had - he grew -
 he used to give it way you know he never ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 He didn't bring it home for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 He'd bring it home but he'd never sell anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What did you do on Bank Holidays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh, I - I always used to think that day was flat you know. There wasn't 
much. Well, you was eating up the old turkey and everybody was half doped sort of thing. I used to think that - I just did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What about August Bank Holidays - what did you do then?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh that wasn't so bad you know. We'd - Hilda and I'd go out. Dad'd go work then you see - August.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Where did you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Heaton Park as a rule you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you go away on a holiday after you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10514531 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh yes. We'd plenty - governments plenty of holidays but they should give you the money to do it with. They'd plenty of holidays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Where did you go to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
Blackpool or Southport when my daughter got grown up she said I'm fed up with going to Blackpool and Southport. I said, your father used to go on extra time to get that money for to take us away. And then - a bit -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you go every year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
Well, that was only one holiday. We used to have about four holidays a year he had but we didn't go away every time. So after she - you know, like one time, since she's been }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10514531 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 , I said why don't you have a few days at Southport 'cos they go in the car and go miles away, perhaps like you do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Why did you choose Blackpool?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, I liked Blackpool. I think the air does you good there - I think it's a nice - although I haven't been for donkeys years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What did you do when Hilda was little when you went to Blackpool?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh, on the sands you mean, you know, me with a deck chair and her with the old bucket and spade - she'd have stopped there all night.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 How did you spend your Saturdays when Hilda was little?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
Well, she used to go out with the kids you know, out at the front and it just depended on what time her father was on and what time he was off, you - you can't live with a man like - men like that that's on different turns you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you do anything special on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, if he was off we'd have a - a trot out but I'm no walker or I've got bad feet when it's hot weather.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What did Hilda do on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, she used to go out with - as she grew up she'd go out with girls you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 When she was little?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, I think they more like - they'd rather play out just outside and get }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6714541\charrsid12273066 
their selves}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066  ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did she attend a place of worship?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes. She was - she used to play the piano at the chapel - at the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you think it was wrong to play on Sundays or work on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
I did - yes. I don't - I can't hear lads playing football and they're here all day Sunday doing that. Get to Sunday school. She went at morning - she played for the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6714541\charrsid12273066 children\rquote s}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066  service then she went in the afternoon - played for the others. Then she went to chapel with me at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You always went to chapel did you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did your husband go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No, I - I used to have to cut his sandwiches up before I went to that chapel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Sometimes he would be working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh working - working nearly every Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you belong to the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did the church run a temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh yes. Hilda used to go. Hilda used to go to that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Were you a member of it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No. I couldn't go anywhere. I was stick with father when I'd got to see him off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You didn't belong to any clubs at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 I don't - I don't - I don't now. I don't now. I tried one or two but - I broke off - I didn't like them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You said that Hilda went to Sunday school - did she go to any of the adult services with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes, at night. Yes, Sunday night, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you say grace at meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes. Yes. Well, I thought it taught Hilda you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you have family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Was Hilda taught to say prayers and who taught her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes, she used to get that at Sunday school you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 The Sunday school taught her to say them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did your husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 He'd no time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you vote in a general election before 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 We'd always vote. We're having another one aren't we.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Do you remember what party he voted for in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 I don't know. Oh, I couldn't tell you that. I don't know. But we were always Conservative you know, our family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you feel that your husband was under pressure to vote for any particular candidate because of his job?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes, yes. Yes, I think they did to a certain extent you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Which party did they think he should vote for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
Conservative. He used to do - yes. Yes. Well his father was Conservative, his mother was Conservative, my father was Conservative and so was me mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You don't think he voted that way just because of his job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, he would never say - I don't know you know he was a bit .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 He didn't take part in a political party or activity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 When you were not doing your work how did you spend your time. - did you go out together in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes. Not - not too often though. I don't think he was a man that - I think to - he liked his own life.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 He liked home life did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Where did you go when you did go out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, perhaps go and sit in Manley Park and he'd have a little bowl - he'd be on to the bowling from the works you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 So he took part in sport?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 The bowling.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You didn't take part in any sport?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 I once tried it but I didn't like - I - I bowled once. We went on 
a picnic once, but he didn't want to go. I said now come on. He says, well I'm not going without you go. I said, well I'll go. And we went and they had a bowl - a bowl - the men and then - they said now in the interval we'll have one for the ladies. So al
l the ladies had to go in whether they could bowl or not. Well, we were all a lot of mugs and I won a prize. He thought I was marvelous.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 But it didn't make you take up sport?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No. I had a bad back all the next day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 So you just used to go to the park?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
Yes. And I'd sit there and watch them bowl. And we had another couple - well, they were really friends of my daughters and they used to play tennis. And then we'd mind the little boy for them while Hilda and her - this husband that she's got
 now and the other two - they'd go on the tennis and I'd sit there and watch them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did either of you ever have a bet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you belong to a savings club of any kind - a boot club or a sick club or a funeral club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No. I had funeral c
lub but I come out of it because I was old - I'm old now and I don't pay. That's all. My husband says it's - it's keeping a lazy lot of lounging people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 How many evenings a week would he spend at home when he wasn't working?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, he - you'd be
 prepared like to go out somewhere - he's finishing at six. And then he phones up to say I'm not coming back 'til nine or ten. You couldn't arrange to go anywhere properly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 So you never knew what evenings he'd be in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No. Or I'd phone up their pl
ace to see if he's coming home about ten o'clock at night. No, so-and-so's not turned in and he's not coming at home all night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you ever go to theatres or concerts or music-halls or cinemas anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, well, we'd - if there was - if there was an odd picture you know that was any good - it's all a lot of rubbish now I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you never go to music-hall in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh we used to do to Manchester you know - were first }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10514531 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 . You know to the Palace and those we'd go an odd time. But we hadn't got much money you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you have any hobbies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, he had his garden and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you have any?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No, I - I - seem as though I was left out of it with not being able to go - you know - regular sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 I know you kept a dog now?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Our old Dutch.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you ever have any interests outside the home - you or your husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No, not really. We were a home people. We were all right so long as we were in and kids playing on the floor and fa
ther's reading his paper. I used to often look at him - you know, I think well he didn't get much time off work you know and reckoned to go to the Devonshire pictures - that's at Leicester Road. We'd go at Saturday night and - first house and we'd come ba
ck then and - he'd have half an hour at the paper and so would I and we'd have our supper then. That's if he got a night off you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you ever go out by yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No. Not that I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did anyone outside the house help you to look after the home when you were first }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10514531 Married}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066  - relations or friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh, they did - yes. But then there was nothing to do - no work to do - everything was new and - all -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 If you were ill what happened?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh well we had to ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What happened when your baby was born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
His mother came. She came at night because - and then I was ill all - all that night and dad was at work you see - nights - on nights. I said I bet it'll come off when he's on night. Well, I was like that for about three days. 
And then - it didn't come off at night - it come off in the afternoon. When his mother had just gone home to see to the family. She had a bus and I had to go while she was away. They had to bring the old doctor and a neighbour down below went for him.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You had a doctor for the birth?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Doctor Johnson - the old family doctor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 And you didn't know at all what to expect?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No. Clowes Street he lived you know. And then in the end he }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10514531 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066  his - his dispensary - his dispensary. But he was very old when he got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10514531 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You said that people outside the home sometimes helped you - relatives - what did they do to help you in the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, they'd come and wash up and clean the windows and ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 This was if you were ill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes. And dust. You hadn't got much time to be ill those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you have relatives living nearby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
Oh about a threepenny bus ride. I had a sister when we got there you know - I lived next door but one to me sister. She got me this house that we went in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you see her very often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
Oh yes. But her husband was an awfully delicate fellow. Oh yes he was awful - he had rheumatics. He was in bed for months and I just happened to go in one day and he's shouting Ada, Ada. I says now - I shouted up -
 now what is - is there anything I can get for you, she's just having her tea. Ada, Ada - and he wouldn't tell me - he wouldn't give her a minutes peace. Ooh terrible. I'd've chopped his head off if I'd have got it. Well that wasn't the ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 How much did you see of this sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
Oh, oh, well she would never come in. She wouldn't come in the house when he was in - when he was in their house she had to be there to attend to him. And somebody went to see him one time and they reckon for rheumatic you 
know the worst thing is lemons to give 'em. But somebody told him they'd do him good and he used to have at least six a day. Just absolute - oh he was stupid. And he took ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you have a lot of friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Where did you see them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, they'd come and - see us and then - you can't ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 They'd come just for a drink or a meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
No, they'd come and say - are you free to come a little walk? Well, I couldn't often go a little walk. If you got chance to go a little walk you'd go with your husband. Well, when he's working you couldn't go could you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did they just come on particular days or did they call in casually?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, it was really weekends you know - Saturday or Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you and your husband have the same friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes - no, because you see all his friends were bowlers and that. Well, they don't want to come and sit in anybody's house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 So you had your own friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes, just round about. Two or three of his friends we had were what he worked with you see and they lived in our street.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 So that the people who came to the house would you say that they were your friends or your husbands?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well I think they was joint because they were - lived in the same street you know and I ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did they call in casually or did they have to have an invitation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes, no - they just - they wouldn't have much time because they'd to do a lot of night work you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you ever go out visiting friends or relations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes. Relations we used to go and see you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Both of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, he wouldn't go on his own without me. But we didn't get chance of going anywhere much you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 When you did go people say you always used to make your own amusements in those days. Well wh
en you got together with friends or neighbours how did you enjoy yourself - was it making music or playing games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No, - just sing - they'd play the piano and they'd sing and - do bits - talk - have a talk and - my husband }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6714541\charrsid12273066 didn\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066  drink but if they wan
ted a drink he'd go for him one - he'd go for them - he never drank. And he never used to smoke - he smoked one time and he started with a cough so he threw it up. Well - he start - I said oh you look miserable with not smoking or doing anything. So he st
arted smoking. I said oh, not - that coughs no better. Well, he said, you told me to stop smoking. So I ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 He always did as you told him did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No, but I think he could see that I was right in that respect. Whenever he started smoking he started coughing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Was your house rented at King Street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes, it was six and six a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you see anything of the landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes, every week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What did you think about him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 He was good with us because my husband used to see he got his mail - his mail first in the morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 They lived near to you did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No, he - he - I mean for his work - he worked - my husband delivered Market Street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you have a struggle to make ends meet when you were first }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10514531 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What did you think about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 I thought we were never going to finish buying, like you. Always wanting something.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Was your husband ever ill or out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh no. No, he pretty - sturdily built - yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 So you never had to go to anybody for help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
Oh no. He had a rupture you see and they wanted - doctor wanted him to go and be operated on. He was a bit of a coward - he wouldn't go. And the doctor came and he says to me - you know, he said, if he had that rupture done, he s
aid, had that operation done, he said, it would prolong his life. I said well tell you here and now doctor you're wasting your time I said, he won't have it done. He said, don't you think so? I said, no, I don't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Was he off work with that at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, an odd time he was you see and that was when they - we brought the doctor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did he like his job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
Oh yes. 'Course he thought - got to think he was there that many years that the government couldn't go on without him. He was a very efficien
t man in - he never had any caused for any mistakes or anything like that - he could tell you anything - tell you any street or anywhere.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You said 'Hatton Street - it was a right neighbourhood - why did you say that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well - it got - it was very 
nice when we went there. But it got a bit - mind it didn't get slum - slums like but as people moved and others come in there was - but still, on the whole, it wasn't bad at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You mean there were different types of families?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 How were they different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, some of them were very noisy and of course as they were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10514531 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066  a year or two they'd have kids and they'd never know when to put them to bed. The mothers - told - the mothers died and fathers were there you see and kids had to
 look after themselves. Yes, it just - it did - it deteriorated a lot that street. And they were proper nice houses too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 When you were young do you ever remember if someone did something wrong people might show their disapproval of them - do you remem
ber what they used to do in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, they'd shun them, you know, they wouldn't have anything to do with them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Nothing else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No. No, but they would - they'd make it a bit uncomfortable some of them would. And some would be just the
 other way - they'd sympathise - well, I used to say you can't help 'em by being nasty with them can you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You don't remember anything else but them shunning them? You never saw them make an effigy - a dummy of them or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, they'd just cock their nose up when they saw them out and I used to think that was awful - that's not bringing them up is it. No, no.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Tell me about your life at the vicar's - were you home sick and ....?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh, I was homesick. I didn't like .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Tell me what you didn't like about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well - I - I don't know. I don't think they should have put me in a place of service at thirteen years of age. Makes an old woman of you.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did they treat you well though?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, - I think nowadays that -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Service was hard in those days wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
Yes. And I think - that the - you never get the same chance when it's such as Ministers, you know, they - get their opportunities a different - they have a different type of living I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
I - I don't - well. If a child talked too much it was wrong and - the - kids were nearly frightened to death of doing anything that - you see, and they never went out to play. Of course there was four children or five - there's enough at home
 you know - they used to have a play room and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You say the father was very strict with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh, he was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 And you didn't like this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No, I didn't like it at all because I think they got no child life. And I've - I've been thinking ever
y night lately - I can't think of his name. He was a Scotchman. He was all right with me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 He treated you well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What did he call you and what did you call him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 I tried to call - I tried to think of his name but - 'course you call him Mr you know - didn't call him Reverend.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What did he call you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 He used to say Susan to me. 'cos I'm Susan - Susan Alice you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Was he strict with the children at meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh Lord, aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Who taught their children what was right and wrong - did you or did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, I think it gradually come with them you see when they sat at the table they knew what they had to do before they get to the table.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You didn't have meals with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh no. Wouldn't have meals with t
hem - we used to be in the kitchen. Used to have a new maid pretty often because - they wouldn't put up with the missus - she was .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What was wrong with the missus?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Missus - yes. Oh well, I think she - I think she felt her position. She was a
 parsons wife you know - and like a lot of other people do - they show their authority. She used to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did she do it with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No, I - I seemed to get on pretty well with her but if the kids did anything wrong you know it was my fault.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You always had to get up with them in the night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh yes. Take 'em out to the park morning afternoon and night. I was fed up with it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you feel that they were interested in you as a person?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes, because I - I think that they gave, you know, a bit - with me having no parents you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You think they took more interest in you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 In what ways?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, they'd give way to me whereas with the other one - the general - they used to, you know, be a bit more strict with her. Or wh
ether it was ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did she give you any moral guidance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
Well, no. She had - I think she had enough to teach her own you know. 'Course I used to take 'em out and take 'em to church. Liverpool Street and it's a long way from here and we used to walk there and back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Were you lonely there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh I was - I - you got fed up with it you know, being up at that time in the morning and ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What time did you say you were up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Six o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What time would you get to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh well you was - after they'd gone to bed you could go if you wanted.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You never did anything else but mind the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No. No. Oh, I'd keep the playroom tidy you know and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You used to do everything for them you said?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 And then you went to work }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4214451\charrsid12273066 in}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066  the shop - did you like the shop - tell me about the shop - what you liked about the shop and what happened there - you only got five shillings a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh we - I did and then if he wasn't about when I was going on me half day on a 
Wednesday I - I thought I can't get any pay he's gone. And next week he wouldn't give me two weeks.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you enjoy the shop work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh I did - yes. There was something going on all the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 It would be the poor district though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Tell me about the poverty that you saw?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh, it was dreadful poverty round there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 How would this affect the people when they came into the shop to buy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, if they - if they say - give us so-and-so and - only we've only got so-and-so. I
 suppose they were getting something out for a pint at night you see, we haven't got any more Alice can you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4214451\charrsid12273066 strap}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066  me }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4214451\charrsid12273066 until the}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12273066  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
weekend. I said you let on about this I says I'll get thrown out. They would but they come up with it on the slate 'til Saturday. Oh there was a lot of drink though - lot of boozing. Yes, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 And you felt the money went on drink sometimes instead of on food?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh yes - on food - yes, the kids'd be walking about with hardly any shoes and the father and mother would be ther
e for the old drink at night. I used to go for chips and fish at twelve o'clock - after twelve at Saturday night and see the same men and women there be blind drunk. The man say - he refused us fish and there's Alice there getting four lovely place. They 
u
sed to cook them for us at chip shop. And he used to be - if - if they'd have had their way they'd have taken that fish and they'd have taken it and left us without. The man at the shop said by gum Alice, and all that lot deserve a fish at this time and i
t were nearly one o'clock in the morning. This - up }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4214451\charrsid12273066 again}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066  - open Sunday morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You saw a lot of drunkeness round there did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh, there was a lot of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Do you think it affected the families?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, he used to like a drop you know, 
the old fellow. Him that would pinched - my sister-in-law - my sister went and took what she thought was a big coin out of his pocket 'cos he'd had a drink or two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Who was this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 My sister - the missus of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Took it off the husband you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
He come in one night you see - always had a bag in his pocket and it was full of sovereigns you see. Wherever he went - purse he had - yes. So anyway he come in one night and - he'd had a drink or two - but he was never awkward - very good with me 
when I was ill. And he come in and - sometimes some of these sovereigns would drop out of the bag you see. So she says are you going to bed? He said Yes. So when he got into bed and she saw him go to sleep she was down where this bag was and she felt some
t
hing loose so it was sovereigns coming out of bag you see. She gets hold of two - so when - I don't know whether I'd gone to bed or not - hey, she says - some sovereigns come out of bag she says and I've pinched two out but I've put them under the bed 'ti
l morning you see, it was dark then. Next morning I said are we going on with this sovereign. She said, it was two threepenny bits.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did she get a wage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh no. No. She worked - yes. He got the profit - plenty of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 He got the profit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 H
e did. And her. He gave - you know she was - she had a bit of money in the stores you see - in the stores in - she said - when she was going a bit peculiar she said to me, Alice, there's an old teapot in that cupboard, she said, and it's got the receipt o
u
t for that money at the co-op - go and draw it out and you have it for yourself. Well, I couldn't draw it out - I wouldn't attempt to draw it out but irrespective of that it would have to have her signature. So I said all right, thank you very much. So th
ere was nothing else said 'til that thing - nobody knew where that was what it was or anything you see. So of course she died and then I told him them, I said, there's a - he didn't do anything about it. Oooh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 She put money away on the quiet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 There was two or three thousand in that blooming -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 She must have taken it out of the shop?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
Save up you see - no, you see, when he gave her that extra money to have the washing done - all that went away you see. And he used to have thick coats on t
he bed to keep us warm - and eiderdown was - no, there was no time - there was no eiderdown. We'd have two or three old - well I think that was poverty when she'd got - money - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Was it a good life living with your sister and her husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 It was nice - well, there was plenty going on - and you knew everybody.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Were they good to you - you'd no mother to go home to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No. Then I had a gastric stomach you see. They - he looked after me better than she did. I had to go on ice and water you
 see, sucking ice. Of course it was the old fashioned recipe. And - he used to turn that horse and cart but to go to Shudehill Market to get ice for me to suck on a Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 He was good to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 He was. He wouldn't bring me a bunch of flowers - he'd bring me a box like you put - set out in the shop - yes. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yet he wouldn't give you your wages?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Crafty - dead crafty that. I don't know whether he just did it - but I never got it you know. Still I didn't mind - I was never short of m
oney.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 But when you came out of service you had no home to go to so you had to go to your sister's?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh yes. Well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Tell me about your childhood with being left an orphan - what was the worst part of it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 All of it - you see - yes. They don't -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What was it like in those days to be left an orphan?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, I don't think it's quite as bad as it is now but - it's -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 How do you mean it wasn't as bad as it is now - I would have thought it was worse?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No, really, 'cos people'd 
help you a bit you know that - out of sympathy sort of thing. Lady across the shop that used to be manageress of Measons toffee shop - her and her daughter were there. Well, when I was ill the first one to take me out was the mother - in a deck - in a cha
ir - wheeling me about. Yes, they were all very good. And I couldn't put shoes on me feet you see, I couldn't do with the weight of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What was the matter with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Gastric ulcer - and it bursted. And he burst it and I was in bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 What difference did it make to your mother being left an orphan in those days - it must have been a very hard life for her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes, it must. She'd have - well, you don't realize it do you - but I think about that many a time. And when I - I was in bed you see 
upstairs, well they hadn't much chance to - to - they did look after me but it - you know, they'd do it but they'd never be able to sit upstairs with you and ulcers bursted. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Was this when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes. When - I was about - eleven I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 This was when your mother was a live was it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
Soon after me mother died this was. And I went to them in the shop you see. And they could hear bumps they come upstairs and it was the burst - the ulcers had burst and I was sick on the floor you see and they could hear the bumps.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Did you go into hospital?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
No, I was too - too - too ill to be moved. And the doctor had an assistant you knew. Doctor used to come in the morning - about an hour after the assistant would come. I say well doctor }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4214451\charrsid12273066 
Johnson\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066  been. Well, I can come as well. And he used to come after and he says - I said to him do you think I'd have been better in hospital? He said no, we daren't move you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 But you eventually got cured of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, my sister you se
e she - she was a bit hard you know, and I should have gone on light food and that see - and he used to turn that horse and cart Sunday morning and all to get fish out of the freezer at the market for me. Lemon soles - they're an expensive thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Your
 mother died when you were eleven and you went to your sister at the greengrocers then and then you went on to the vicar after that did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 And then you came back from the vicar's to your sister because it was too much at the vicar's was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes, yes. It was, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You said that in the end you got fed up and felt that your sister didn't want you with her when she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10514531 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066  didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes, yes. Then she died that terrible death. Oh, she had a terrible time. I - I'll never forget it - hope I never go a bit queer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 But you had a hard life as a whole?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 I have had a hard life. You have to do when you're left without parents aren't you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Your mother must have had it worse though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Oh, my mother had - she didn't get much ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Were you frightened as a child when you knew you'd no father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Not 'til I got older you see. We -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 When you got about what age?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 About thirteen - I got to feel, you know, I felt that I'd had no life - I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 This was when you went to work for the vicar wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 I'll - ooh - I'll never forget that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You were frightened when you first went?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Mm. Well, with only being a child you - I think it was awful that. I think they could have afforde
d to have - but they didn't bother you know and ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 You think they could have afforded to what - to have kept you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Do you mean your sister or the vicar?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No, me sister could have done different really. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4214451\charrsid12273066 But then when she got
 like she died like she did you have to swallow a lot to think that she wasn't - yes, and she'd nothing - she'd no worries at all. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 
I don't know what made her go like that. 'Cos there was nothing ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 It was really through your sister when you were young that you went to the vicarage was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Because she was difficult to get on with or something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Well, what I mean like when you got older - found out then that it was her nerves you see. You couldn't expect her - she used to
 have awful bothers with her husband. We used to sell bloaters in the shop, you know, like - and she said something to him one day in the shop and he got hold of one of these and attempted to hit her with it and it caught - the end of it caught her and - 
ooh, she was in a terrible state. I think it was that that was started her off you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 And you think she had bad nerves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 Yes, that - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12530893 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 But service in those days - you read quite a lot about it - you didn't like it obviously did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid655614 SF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516112\charrsid12273066 No.
\par }}